rhopgradient.comment: Initial density gradient 1:Rhop0, 2:Water column, 3:Max. water height (default=2)

hswl.comment: Maximum still water level to calculate speedofsound using coefsound

gamma.comment: Polytropic constant for water used in the state equation

speedsystem.comment: Maximum system speed (by default the dam-break propagation is used)

hdp.comment: Alternative option to calculate the smoothing length (h=hdp*dp)

theory.comment: Theory of generation 1:Rayleigh (Serre 1953), 2: Boussinesq (Goring 1978) 3: KdV (Clamond and Germain 1999) (def=2)

savemotion.comment: Saves motion data. xpos is optional for elevation calculation
